{{History of Angola}}
The '''Arquivo Histórico Nacional''' is the [[national archive]] of [[Angola]]. Overseen by the {{illm|Government of the Republic of Angola|pt|Governo da República de Angola|lt=Ministry of Culture}}[http://www.mincultura.gv.ao/mapa_do_site.htm], it is headquartered in the city of [[Luanda]] on Rua Pedro Felix Machado. As of 2016 a new archives building was under construction in [[Camama]].<ref>{{citation |url=http://www.mincult.gov.ao/vernoticia.aspx?id=31285 |title=Ministra visita obras do novo edifício do Arquivo Nacional |trans-title=Minister visits site of the new National Archives building |work= Mincult.gov.ao |publisher=Governo de Angola |language=pt |date=15 October 2016 }}</ref> The Arquivo Histórico Nacional originated in the Centro Nacional de Documentação e Investigação Histórica.[https://books.google.com/books?id=-ugXmJeQMaYC&pg=PA2]

